DexOffline is an application that helps you find words in DEX (the Romanian language dictionary) without being online, play Hangman, Pheasant or Wordle games and much more.

Features:
- Search words in offline and online Romanian dictionaries (you can change the search strategy from Settings);
- Possibility to search exactly the words with diacritics if the quotation marks are used;
- Save the searched words;
- Check if a word is in the official word list for the Scrabble game;
- Browse and filter the words in the dictionary;
- Read the feed with words of the day;
- Play Hangman game (you can configure the length of the guess word in Settings);
- Play Pheasant game (write the word that starts with the last 2 letters of the previous word);
- Play Wordle game (guess the word from at most 6 tries, green letter means the letter was matched in the right position, yellow letter means the letter is in the word, but not in the right position);
- Ability to change the display language and choose a dark theme from Settings.

All suggestions to improve the app and add new functionality are welcome.

